UID:raiFmx-3iVdcVnIxirHjI
SUMMARY:ALOK: Eat Pray Leave Tour
DTSTAMP:20260629T025255Z
DTSTART:20260629T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:Doors will open one hour prior to show time. This show is 18 & 
	over with valid\, government-issued photo ID. There is a two beverage mini
	mum per person. Cameras and video/audio recording devices are not permitte
	d. $.25 per each ticket sold for a majority of events at Punch Line benefi
	ts Comedy Gives Back\, a safety net for the comedy community. For more inf
