	rder. Look for the logo on the Find Tickets page to view all available acc
	essible seats. We do have accessible seating in every price range but be a
	dvised it may sell out. We have very limited seating available for guests 
	on the day of the event so please make sure you purchase accessible seatin
	g when you order tickets. Bags up to 12" x 6" x 12" are allowed in the ven
	ue. All bags will be searched prior to entry. For more FAQs please visit w
	ww.houston.houseofblues.com/faq\nBOX OFFICE:6PM DOORS: 7PM All Ages Welcom
