	d up on day of show at the Box Office. Box Office opens 1 hour prior to do
	or times. You will need a valid photo ID and the credit card used for purc
	hase. ADA tickets can be purchased online - you do not need to call the bo
	x office to place an order. Look for the logo on the Find Tickets page to 
